window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Unearthing the past could destroy the future. Fin Brooks races against time itself.</b></p> <p>When the Rot spreads to an Accord-protected planet, Yormanth, Ranger Fin Brooks and the ragtag Black Sheep crew plunge into action. But what begins as a mission to save one world quickly spirals into an ancient mystery that threatens the entire galaxy.</p> <p>Old criminal rivals are already a step ahead of Fin and the Rangers. They know what lies buried beneath treacherous jungles, prehistoric alien ruins, and deep, subterranean oceans teeming with dangerous secrets.</p> <p>Echoes of the past haunt the galaxy. History threatens to repeat.</p> <p>Battling murderous monsters, outsmarting devious enemies, and somehow keeping his ship—and sanity—intact, Fin must unlock the secrets of a long-lost civilization before it's too late. The fate of worlds hangs in the balance, and failure isn't just death—it's extinction.</p> <p><b>Book 5 of this rollicking sci-fi adventure from Anthony J. Melchiorri. It's perfect for fans of JN Chaney, MR Forbes, and </b><b><i>The Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy.</i></b></p>"; 
